        RSEG XDATA_I:XDATA:NOROOT(0)
        DATA32
__Constant_10000:
        DS 4
        REQUIRE `?<Initializer for __Constant_10000>`
        REQUIRE __INIT_XDATA_I

        RSEG XDATA_ID:CODE:NOROOT(0)
`?<Initializer for __Constant_10000>`:
        DATA32
        DD 65536

        RSEG XDATA_I:XDATA:NOROOT(0)
        DATA32
__Constant_ffff:
        DS 4
        REQUIRE `?<Initializer for __Constant_ffff>`
        REQUIRE __INIT_XDATA_I

        RSEG XDATA_ID:CODE:NOROOT(0)
`?<Initializer for __Constant_ffff>`:
        DATA32
        DD 65535

        RSEG BANK_RELAYS:CODE:REORDER:NOROOT(0)
??ldr_init?relay:
        LCALL   ?BDISPATCH
        DATA
        DC24    ldr_init

        RSEG BANK_RELAYS:CODE:REORDER:NOROOT(0)
??ldr_read_lux?relay:
        LCALL   ?BDISPATCH
        DATA
        DC24    ldr_read_lux

        END
